Massmart Files Papers on Planned Purchase of Fruitspot, Business Day Says

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-12T05:15:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/massmart-files-papers-on-planned-purchase-of-fruitspot-business-day-says.html
Massmart Holdings Ltd. (MSM)  plans to
purchase The Fruitspot, a fresh produce supplier, Business Day
reported, citing Massmart spokesman Brian Leroni.  The retailer made an application to South African antitrust
authorities regarding the acquisition, the Johannesburg-based
newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  